696
00:55:45,914 --> 00:55:52,316
Surrounding communities are offering tax incentives to local businesses and small businesses to attract them.

697
00:55:53,037 --> 00:55:55,518
They're trying to attract a variety of business

698
00:55:55,955 --> 00:56:02,056
So you just don't have, you know, all of one particular business or two different type of businesses.

699
00:56:02,837 --> 00:56:08,558
That makes it more attractive for people that want to come in and traverse the downtown business districts.

700
00:56:09,578 --> 00:56:18,320
A few months ago, I offered a resolution to look at the transportation shelter across from the CVS on Riverside Ave.

701
00:56:18,800 --> 00:56:23,301
We got a response back from the administration saying they'll take it under advisement.

702
00:56:24,540 --> 00:56:28,203
which is, in my opinion, unacceptable, Mr. President.

703
00:56:28,903 --> 00:56:45,574
That particular shelter definitely could be reused for another purpose in our community, whether it be for arts or whether it be for retail or whether it be an inviting place to attract people.

704
00:56:46,014 --> 00:56:53,139
When they did the square of the revitalization plan in the square many years back,

705
00:56:53,977 --> 00:57:04,561
