00:57:32,475 --> 00:57:33,435
The gutters are missing.

712
00:57:34,016 --> 00:57:35,597
The paint's peeling off the side.

713
00:57:36,537 --> 00:57:38,498
It's really not being used at all right now.

714
00:57:39,139 --> 00:57:51,145
And the repurposing of that for another use could have an area where we could have people that would come and sit down and turn it into a vibrant area rather than something that's currently neglected.

715
00:57:51,627 --> 00:57:54,507
But it's long overdue in this community, Mr. President.

716
00:57:55,088 --> 00:57:57,368
We need to sit down with this administration.

717
00:57:58,008 --> 00:58:01,029
The mayor controls the Office of Community Development.

718
00:58:01,549 --> 00:58:17,071
And in my opinion, you know, I don't want to be critical of anyone in particular, but in my opinion, that department is sorely understaffed and is not serving the purpose of a community development office like I see happening in other communities.

