965
01:16:59,257 --> 01:16:59,998
He was a good guy.

966
01:17:00,018 --> 01:17:01,098
He comes from a good family.

967
01:17:02,039 --> 01:17:05,582
His wife, Sharon, Sam Sawyer.

968
01:17:08,208 --> 01:17:17,134
I don't know what to say other than the fact that he was, you know, it was, it's one of these times in your life that something happens and you just can't explain it.

969
01:17:17,274 --> 01:17:19,955
And, um, but I'm not going to try to explain it right now.

970
01:17:19,995 --> 01:17:22,977
