971
01:17:23,357 --> 01:17:23,938
We all thank you.

972
01:17:26,019 --> 01:17:26,740
Councilor Camuso.

973
01:17:27,400 --> 01:17:28,441
Thank you, Mr. President.

974
01:17:28,581 --> 01:17:31,222
And, uh, Steven was also a great personal friend of mine.

975
01:17:31,422 --> 01:17:32,423
Uh, just a great guy.

976
01:17:33,103 --> 01:17:37,006
And, uh, as we all know, his family goes back, uh, 50 years of public service.

977
01:17:37,517 --> 01:17:49,805
whether it was his dad, Frank, working for the Sheriff's Department back as a superintendent in the 1980s and the 70s, his mom, Roberta, who still works here part-time and does a fabulous job, his brother, Frank.

978
01:17:50,005 --> 01:17:52,587
He's also with the MBTA.

979
01:17:53,027 --> 01:17:55,109
Just a great, great, great family.

