01:21:34,666 --> 01:21:49,976
And when the time comes for us to have meetings, uh, should this process start to move further, then, uh, that, that opportunity will present itself and we'll be on the forefront of that, uh, as, uh, counselors,

1022
01:21:50,693 --> 01:21:53,435
protecting the interests of providers up there.

